                            <comment id="13836037" author="shalinmangar" created="Sun, 1 Dec 2013 14:55:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Adding support for shards.tolerant in StatsComponent and SpellCheckComponent. Added tests in TestDistributedSearch as well.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
